getEGContentCellContent

@Deprecated
public java.util.List<java.lang.Object> getEGContentCellContent()
Deprecated. 

Gets the value of the egContentCellContent property.

This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the egContentCellContent property.

For example, to add a new item, do as follows: 

    getEGContentCellContent().add(newItem);
